title: SCION Samplers Vol. 1-8
description:
This is the first 8 of a series of music sampler CDs the SCION car company put out, supposedly to demonstrate the capabilities of the stereo systems in their vehicles.

I will say, there's some fuckin' bangin' music on these discs, and I've discovered a lot of kickass artists/groups as a result of listening to them. Royksopp, Dakah Hip-Hop Orchestra, Felix Da Housecat and N*E*R*D just to name a few.

All songs are in mp3 format with a 128 bit rate. Don't like it? Don't download it.
